Make sure the antlr.jar and commons-cli-1.0.jar (in the "classes"
directory) and this directory are in your CLASSPATH

Use the following commands to compile and test the program:

$ make grammar
$ make
$ java Java2CodeML tests/LongTest.java

Java2CodeML generates unformatted XML output. To pretty print it,
pipe it through xmllint like:

$ java Java2CodeML test/LongTest.java | xmllint --format -
